## Goal
Single index for all hackathon handoff `.plan` files — priorities, status, next session entry point.

## Why it matters for judges (scoring rubric tie-in)
Judges score **Autonomy 30%**, **Creativity 30%**, **Technical 20%**. P0 items directly prove autonomous multi-agent + live demo + clean submission.

